data.description: This manufactured home offers an excellent location! The picturesque neighborhood of Dogwood Acres is less than 4 miles to Walmart, less than 15 minute drive to WCU, and under 30 minute drive to Harrah's Cherokee Casino Resort!  This home has so much to offer indoors and out. The outdoor space of this home is very spacious and includes a great workshop. There is plenty of flat space in the back yard for a small garden or additional storage buildings. This interior has a wonderful split floorplan. On one side of the home is the master bedroom with a large bath and the other side of the home are the 2 spare bedrooms with a 2nd full bath. Washer and dryer hook ups are off of the kitchen that includes a refrigerator, stove, and microwave. This property is being sold as is. Please contact the listing agent directly with any questions or showing requests.
